      <h2>1. Product Authenticity, Ownership & Sales</h2>
      <p>
        All products displayed, cataloged, and showcased on this website are the direct, authentic offerings of
        <strong>Spicery Co.</strong> We hold complete ownership, authorization, and rights to sell and distribute all
        types of products listed in our store.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our collection includes premium ground spices, whole peppercorns, custom seasoning blends, botanical herbs, and
        artisanal salts. We guarantee that every product image, ingredient list, and packaging specifications represent
        our genuine inventory, sourced from ethical agricultural cooperatives and certified farmers worldwide.
      </p>

      <h2>2. Editorial Integrity: 100% Expert & Human-Made Blogs</h2>
      <p>
        We believe that true culinary wisdom comes from real kitchen experience. Therefore, we enforce a strict
        editorial policy for our <strong>Aromatic Journal</strong>:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Culinary Expertise:</strong> All recipes, spice guides, historical highlights, and kitchen tips are
