        alteration, or distribution of your information. We never sell, rent, or distribute your email addresses or
        personal information to third-party advertisers.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Cookies & Tracking Preferences</h2>
      <p>
        Our website uses browser cookies to remember your display preferences and page histories. You have the right to
        disable cookies through your individual browser settings; however, doing so may affect certain interactive
